The Wallbox Pulsar Plus is one of the most stylish home EV chargers you can buy. It's compact, well-designed, and comes with an app that's genuinely easy to use. But in a UK market increasingly dominated by smart tariff integration and energy optimisation, does looking good and being simple still cut it?

We've dug into the specs, the app, the pricing, and — crucially — the customer support situation to give you the full picture.

